// ─── VADPRS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// Vanderbilt ADHD Diagnostic Parent Rating Scale
// Questions 1–47: frequency scale (Never / Occasionally / Often / Very Often)
// Questions 48–55: performance scale (Excellent–Problematic) — 5 options, same count
